### TransitOps API — living contract & test file
### Base URL for all requests; Bobby: same value as NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001/api

### Health check — verifies server + database connectivity
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Unknown route — demonstrates the standard error envelope
GET {{baseUrl}}/does-not-exist


### ==================== AUTH (Module 2) ====================

### Register: Fleet Manager
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Fatima Khan",
  "email": "fleet@transitops.dev",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "FLEET_MANAGER"
}

### Register: Driver (dispatcher persona per problem statement)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alex Verma",
  "email": "driver@transitops.dev",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "DRIVER"
}

### Register: Safety Officer
